data.description: Location! Location! Welcome to the Tuscan Floorplan plan by Blackrock Homes in the gorgeous Verado community. This property lives larger than the square-footage. Rich cabinetry w/ tile backsplash, granite counters throughout and a large walk-in pantry. HOA includes landscape maintenance and water, yard mowing, and sprinkler repair. Come enjoy a low maintenance lifestyle in this well kept community with walking trails and a lovely community park.
